-- year() equals toYear(today()), toYear(now()) and year(today())
1	1	1
-- result type is UInt16
UInt16
-- current year is a sane value
1
-- case-insensitive
1	1	1
-- year() is non-deterministic (evaluated once at analysis, like today())
1
-- year(<date>) still works as the deterministic alias of toYear
2023	1900	2077	2149
-- two-argument toYear(datetime, timezone) is unaffected
2023
-- the rewrite year() -> toYear(today()) is visible in EXPLAIN SYNTAX (analyzer-agnostic)
1
